## 5. Environment Variables

All secrets and config live in a `.env` file at project root. Never commit this file.

```
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./data/stockresearch.db
DEFAULT_DATE_OFFSET_DAYS=3
APP_PORT=8000
```

`GEMINI_API_KEY` is automatically aliased to `GOOGLE_API_KEY` at startup вЂ” `langchain-google-genai` (used internally by TradingAgents) expects the latter. No manual renaming needed.

Model selection (`deep_think_llm`, `quick_think_llm`) is persisted in the `app_config` database table and managed via `PATCH /api/config`, not via env vars.

