## 8. Frontend Pages & Components

### 8.1 New Analysis Page (default/home)

- **Ticker input** вЂ” text field, auto-uppercases, validates against basic format (1вЂ“5 letters)
- **Date picker** вЂ” defaults to today minus `DEFAULT_DATE_OFFSET_DAYS`, user can override to any past date. Future dates not selectable.
- **Run button** вЂ” submits the request, disables during run
- **Progress indicator** вЂ” polls `/api/runs/{id}/status` every 5 seconds, shows current agent activity message (e.g. вЂњFundamental analyst workingвЂ¦вЂќ)
- **Result card** вЂ” appears inline when run completes, showing recommendation badge + summary thesis. Link to full report.

### 8.2 History Page

- **Runs table** вЂ” columns: Ticker, Analysis Date, Run Date, Recommendation (colour-coded badge), Actions
- **Search/filter** вЂ” filter by ticker text input
- **Click row** в†’ opens Run Detail Page
- **Delete button** per row with confirmation

### 8.3 Run Detail Page

- Header: Ticker, analysis date, recommendation badge, run timestamp
- **Tabs:**
  - **Summary** вЂ” final trader report / investment thesis (full text)
  - **Fundamentals** вЂ” fundamental analyst report
  - **Sentiment** вЂ” sentiment analyst report
  - **Technical** вЂ” technical analyst report
  - **Risk** вЂ” risk team assessment
  - **Raw** вЂ” full JSON dump of stored data
- Back button to History

### 8.4 Settings Page

- **Deep think model** вЂ” dropdown (`gemini-2.5-pro` / `gemini-2.5-flash`); used by complex reasoning agents (Portfolio Manager, Risk team). Calls `PATCH /api/config` on change.
- **Quick think model** вЂ” dropdown (`gemini-2.5-flash` / `gemini-2.5-pro`); used by faster utility agents. Calls `PATCH /api/config` on change.
- **Default date offset** вЂ” read-only display sourced from `GET /api/config`; user edits `.env` to change it.
- Link to Gemini API console

