## 9. Background Job Behaviour

- On `POST /api/runs`, a run record is created immediately with `status=pending`
- FastAPI BackgroundTasks picks it up and calls `TradingAgentsGraph.propagate(ticker, date)`
- Status updates to `running` when the job starts
- On success: status в†’ `complete`, all fields populated
- On failure: status в†’ `failed`, `error_message` populated
- Runs are **not queued** вЂ” if a run is already in `running` state, new submissions are accepted but will run concurrently. For personal use this is fine. Consider adding a warning in the UI if a run is already active.

