## 13. Error Handling

|Scenario                  |Behaviour                                                                                                    |
|--------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Gemini API rate limit hit |Status в†’ `failed`, error message shown in UI with retry button                                               |
|Invalid ticker            |TradingAgents returns error в†’ caught, stored, shown in UI                                                    |
|DS218+ loses power mid-run|On next startup, any run still in `running` state is immediately marked `failed` with message вЂњServer restarted while this run was in progress.вЂќ The `started_at` column is available if finer-grained stale detection is needed in future.|
|Gemini API key missing    |App refuses to start (`GEMINI_API_KEY` / `GOOGLE_API_KEY` checked in lifespan hook), logs clear error message|
|Future date submitted     |`POST /api/runs` returns HTTP 422 вЂ” analysis_date cannot be in the future                                    |

